		<title>Amazon shows off Alexa feature that mimics the voices of your dead relatives</title>
		<link>https://hoangtronganh.github.io/amazon-shows-off-alexa-feature-that-mimics-the-voices-of-your-dead-relatives/</link>
					<comments>https://hoangtronganh.github.io/amazon-shows-off-alexa-feature-that-mimics-the-voices-of-your-dead-relatives/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 30 Jun 2022 06:22:58 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Artificial Intelligence]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Amazon]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Tech]]></category>
